narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Depaul Community Resources is a Foster Care Agency provider based in Roanoke, VA. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $86.6M in Medicaid payments across 25K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $86.6M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
